reviews.review_text:
Nice crisp 85 show Crisp aud recording. Wind and Phil's bass disturb but a sweet Cryptical and Fire ..

Better than tonys and mccue.ford.

My First Show w/ BACKSTAGE PASSES!!! I lived in Venice at the time and my neighbor, Wendy (a Dead legal employee) said lets go to see the Dead in Ventura , I was not a head at the time.....So we drove up, expecting to get in free, and the gal at the will call shack reeled off 7 backstage passes! I didn't have a deep knowledge of their music, but had a great time. After the show, we were sitting at some tables in this circle of trailers behind the stage, and there was Bob, standing alone with a glass of wine. I decided to say hi, good show, to which he replied " Naw, we were wasted"
